projects.projectDescription: I worked with Johnson and Johnson Innovations on a grant with Rutgers Data Science Consulting as a Computer Science Project Lead. Our goal was to develop a system for generating survey results in PDF format for innovators who have taken the Health Equity Assessment Tool. My role on the project was to design a mockup of the report, develop the system for generating the personalized reports, and push the new PDF reports to J&J Innovationâ€™s server via SFTP.
